pizzaProgram.events
Class EventType

java.lang.Object
  pizzaProgram.events.EventType

public class EventType
extends Object

A class containing constants representing event types. ALL objects dispatching events should use constants from this class to represent event types.

Author:
IT1901 Group 3, Fall 2011
